      "content": "That's a lot of dismissive language. I'm just trying to get a neutral overview for a research paper. Can you be more objective and actually list the names of some of the prominent researchers or the specific studies they use to support the idea of biological differences? I want to see the actual evidence they present so I can critique it properly.",
